        <h3>2012 Annual Conference<br />
        </h3>
    <p>June 14–16, 2012<br />
            <a href="http://www.seventhmountain.com/" target="_blank">Seventh Mountain Resort, </a>Bend<br />
        </p>
    <p><br />
      <strong>Online registration is now closed. </strong>Please call the OCDLA office, 541-686-8716, or register at the door at Seventh Mountain Resort on Thursday.<br />
    </p>
