            <td height="64" align="left" valign="top" class="cart-blankline"><p>4:00</p></td>
            <td align="left" valign="top" class="cart-blankline"><p><span class="style24"><strong>Stops: The Appellate Zone</strong><br />
The Honorable Michael McShane and The Honorable Eric Bergstrom, Multnomah County Circuit Court</span><br />
</p>
              <p class="style24"><em>The OCDLA actors guild, directed by Judges McShane and Bergstrom, bring back the classic theater of Broadway in this six-act representation of the tragic world of Rogers and Kirkeby, two star-struck lovers pulled over at the cosmic intersection of Search Lane and Seizure Boulevard.  Come see the Court of Appeals brought to life before your eyes in The Case of the Curious Fertilizer Salesman, Gran Torino, Laverne and Shirley go to Jail, and other classic hits that resemble something you read in the Advance Sheets or something you saw on Nickelodeon late at night while pretending to read the Advance Sheets. </em></p>
              <p class="style24"><em>Groupon discounts will be accepted only during the matinee showing.</em></p>
              <p class="style7">(new day and time)<br />
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td align="left" valign="top" class="cart-blankline"><p>5:00</p></td>
            <td align="left" valign="top" class="cart-blankline"><p>CLE adjourns for the day.<br />
              Transition to Barbecue.</p></td>
